<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>FastAuth OAuth Example</title>
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 50px auto;
				padding: 20px;
			}
			.button {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 12px 24px;
				background-color: #4285f4;
				color: white;
				text-decoration: none;
				border-radius: 4px;
				font-weight: 500;
			}
			.button:hover {
				background-color: #357ae8;
			}
			.section {
				margin: 30px 0;
				padding: 20px;
				background-color: #f5f5f5;
				border-radius: 8px;
			}
			h1 {
				color: #333;
			}
			h2 {
				color: #666;
			}
			code {
				background-color: #e8e8e8;
				padding: 2px 6px;
				border-radius: 3px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>FastAuth OAuth Example</h1>
		<p>This example demonstrates Google OAuth integration with FastAuth.</p>

		<div class="section">
			<h2>Try it out!</h2>
			<a href="/oauth/google/authorize" class="button">Sign in with Google</a>
		</div>

		<div class="section">
			<h2>What this demo shows:</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Google OAuth login flow</li>
				<li>Automatic user creation from OAuth profile</li>
				<li>Linking OAuth accounts to existing users</li>
				<li>Viewing linked OAuth accounts</li>
				<li>Unlinking OAuth accounts</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="section">
			<h2>API Endpoints:</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><code>GET /oauth/google/authorize</code> - Initiate OAuth flow</li>
				<li>
					<code>POST /oauth/google/callback</code> - Handle OAuth callback
				</li>
				<li>
					<code>GET /oauth/accounts</code> - List linked accounts (requires
					auth)
				</li>
				<li>
					<code>DELETE /oauth/accounts/{id}</code> - Unlink account (requires
					auth)
				</li>
				<li><code>GET /profile</code> - View user profile (requires auth)</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="section">
			<h2>Documentation:</h2>
			<p>Visit <a href="/docs">/docs</a> for interactive API documentation</p>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
